race.description: Tabtouch Place A Same Race Multi Mdn
race.comment: MOONWALK (8) is a progressive type on resumption. She showed good ability in her debut campaign as a 2YO and looks well placed in a midweek maiden. Pike was on board for her trial and remains in the saddle for her return. Looks the one to beat down in the weights. DANCEWITHME (4) was strong in tougher company on debut on the back of some handy trials before heading for a break. She has trialled just as good this time around and the gear changes suggests she's matured in the break. Can play a leading role. BONDI LIFESAVER (7) is on debut for the Neville Parnham yard. He's a half-brother to the likes of Listed winner Queen Alina and Chris Parnham has been with him the whole way. Right in the mix if he runs up to his trials. PLAYA DEL SOL (11) has shown some ability at the trials and won't be far away. EXCEED THE BOOM (2) is fitter now and can put his best foot forward.
